description:
Phoenix supports using placeholders in your tags and other settings which utilize text. To use placeholders, use the placeholder name braced like this, {{placeholder}}.
Valid placeholders:
* `mention`: Ping of the user : {{mention}}
* `username`: Username of the user : {{username}}
* `userid`: The id of the user : {{userid}}
* `membercount`: Number of members in the server : {{membercount}}
* `servername`: Name of the server : {{servername}}
